ht</option>\n    </select>\n    <header>Borders</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Borders\" name=\"showBorders\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Borders Color\" name=\"bordersColor\" value=\"#5e5c7e\" condition=\"showBorders\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" required>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"../_images/background2.jpg\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#141229\" selected>\n    </fieldset>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#efefef\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <!--Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title mbr-pb-5\" mbr-class=\"{'align-center':titleAlign==2,\n                         'align-right':titleAlign==3}\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mbr-bold mbr-white\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">Services &amp; Rates</h3>\n            <h4 class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mbr-pt-2 mbr-white\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">Enter your article subtitle here</h4>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mbr-row mbr-pt-5\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-col-sm-12 mbr-col-md-12\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-col-lg-6': cardsAmount > 1,\n                             'mbr-col-lg-12': cardsAmount == 1}\">\n                <div class=\"card-box box1 mbr-flex\">\n                    <div class=\"text-box mbr-white\" mbr-class=\"{'align-center': leftCardsAlign == 2, \n                                     'align-right': leftCardsAlign == 3}\">\n                        <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style text-box-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".text-box-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardsTitle\">Remote Support</h3>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-pt-3 text-box-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".text-box-text\" mbr-if=\"showCardsText\">Ask us about accessing your office from home!<br>We can connect remotely or simply talk you through instructions over the phone to help with the setup of computers, networks, printers, installation of apps, malware removal, how-to's and more. Very basic questions will be answered free of charge in some cases. $15 minimum charge for remote connections - no masks needed!</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"icon-box\" mbr-if=\"showNumberBox\">\n                        <div class=\"round-box round1\">\n                            <div class=\"number-box\">\n                                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-bold mbr-white number-box-number\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".number-box-number\">$69/hr<br></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mbr-col-sm-12 mbr-col-md-12 mbr-col-lg-6\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 1\">\n                <div class=\"card-box box2 mbr-flex\">\n                    <div class=\"text-box mbr-white\" mbr-class=\"{'align-center': rightCardsAlign == 2, \n                                     'align-right': rightCardsAlign == 3}\">\n                        <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style text-box-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".text-box-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardsTitle\">On-Site Support</h3>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-pt-3 text-box-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".text-box-text\" mbr-if=\"showCardsText\">Armed with appropriate PPE and the tools needed for the job, we will come to your home or business and fix all your tech needs in one fell swoop! Give us a chance to look at your setup, tell us what you want out of it and be part of the learning process while we work. Ask us about setting up remote desktop connections so you can access your office from home! $50 minimum service charge.&nbsp;</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"icon-box\" mbr-if=\"showNumberBox\">\n                        <div class=\"round-box round2\">\n                            <div class=\"number-box\">\n                                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-bold mbr-white number-box-number\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".number-box-number\">$89/hr</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mbr-col-sm-12 mbr-col-md-12\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-col-lg-6': cardsAmount > 3,\n                             'mbr-col-lg-12': cardsAmount == 3}\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 2\">\n                <div class=\"card-box box3 mbr-flex\">\n                    <div class=\"text-box mbr-white\" mbr-class=\"{'align-center': leftCardsAlign == 2, \n                                     'align-right': leftCardsAlign == 3}\">\n                        <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style text-box-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".text-box-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardsTitle\">Hardware Repair</h3>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-pt-3 text-box-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".text-box-text\" mbr-if=\"showCardsText\">PAY US ONLY FOR OUR TIME! We don't care to make money on retail products and only charge for our time spent. Bring your own parts or we will find the best price and allow you to purchase them for the repair. On-Site labor is charged in real time, but we will make every effort to be efficient and give you the most cost-effective service. Pick-Ups max out at 2 hours labor and we do not charge for idle time while your computer downloads, updates, installs or scans - only the time spent actually in front of the computer.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"icon-box\" mbr-if=\"showNumberBox\">\n                        <div class=\"round-box round3\">\n                            <div class=\"number-box\">\n                                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-bold mbr-white number-box-number\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".number-box-number\">$89/hr</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mbr-col-sm-12 mbr-col-md-12 mbr-col-lg-6\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 3\">\n                <div class=\"card-box box4 mbr-flex\">\n                    <div class=\"text-box mbr-white\" mbr-class=\"{'align-center': rightCardsAlign == 2, \n                                     'align-right': rightCardsAlign == 3}\">\n                        <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style text-box-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".text-box-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardsTitle\">Custom Gaming Builds</h3>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-pt-3 text-box-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".text-box-text\" mbr-if=\"showCardsText\">We work on custom builds! Bring your own parts or let us help you find the best build for your budget. We use PC Part Picker to shop for the best prices from multiple retailers.The best deals generally come from Newegg and Amazon, but we sometimes find great deals from obscure retailers. Pay us only for our time spent. Most builds average 2hrs labor, but additional time may be needed for custom cooling or lighting.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"icon-box\" mbr-if=\"showNumberBox\">\n                        <div class=\"round-box round4\">\n                            <div class=\"number-box\">\n                                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-bold mbr-white number-box-number\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".number-box-number\">$89/hr</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
